results.name: Molien series for invariants of finite Coxeter group A_9.
comment: The Molien series for the finite Coxeter group of type A_k (k >= 1) has g.f. = 1/Product_{i=2..k+1} (1-x^i).
Note that this is the root system A_k not the alternating group Alt_k.
reference: J. E. Humphreys, Reflection Groups and Coxeter Groups, Cambridge, 1990. See Table 3.1, page 59.
link: Ray Chandler, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000
maple: seq(coeff(series( mul(1/(1-x^j), j=2..10), x, n+1), x, n), n = 0..70); # _G. C. Greubel_, Feb 02 2020
program: (MAGMA) R<x>:=PowerSeriesRing(Integers(), 70); Coefficients(R!( &*[1/(1-x^j): j in [2..10]] )); // _G. C. Greubel_, Feb 02 2020
return P( product(1/(1-x^j) for j in (2..10)) ).list()
xref: Molien series for finite Coxeter groups A_1 through A_12 are A059841, A103221, A266755, A008667, A037145, A001996, and A266776-A266781.
